Video/Info version 0.05
=======================

Generic class to probe video files for various attributes.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test (optional)
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module does not require any other modules or libraries.
However, for Video::Info to be of any use, you should install 
at least one of the following:
   RIFF::Info
   ASF::Info
   MP3::Info
   MPEG::Info

